Create an Areas Object

create_areas.Rd

Constructs and validates an areas object as an S3 class.

create_areas(levels, hierarchy, boundaries)

Arguments

levels

Data frame of area level metadata.
hierarchy

Data frame defining area hierarchy and area-level data.
boundaries

an sf object with boundary geometry for each area_id

Value

An object of class naomi_areas

Examples

data(mwi_area_levels)
data(mwi_area_hierarchy)
data(mwi_area_boundaries)

areas <- create_areas(mwi_area_levels, mwi_area_hierarchy, mwi_area_boundaries)
areas
